							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/dylanpenningroth/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/dylan-c-penningroth-100x100.jpeg" width="100" height="100" alt="Dylan C. Penningroth" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/dylanpenningroth/">Dylan C. Penningroth</a></h6>
										Dylan C. Penningroth is a professor of law and history at the University of California, Berkeley, and he specializes in African American history. He is a recipient of the MacArthur Fellowship and the author of the award-winning book <em>The Claims of Kinfolk.</em>																			</div>
